Name: Classic Guitar
Description: The guitar is a fretted musical instrument that typically has six strings

Name: Acoustic Guitar
Description: An acoustic guitar is a musical instrument in the guitar family

Name: Electric guitar
Description: An electric guitar is a guitar that requires external amplification in order to be heard at typical performance volumes, unlike a standard acoustic guitar.

Name: Bass guitar
Description: The bass guitar, electric bass or simply bass, is the lowest-pitched member of the guitar family.
